	* libltdl/m4/libtool.m4 (_LT_LINKER_SHLIBS)
	(_LT_SYS_DYNAMIC_LINKER): Remove handling of freebsd1* which
	soon would incorrectly match FreeBSD 10.0.
	* NEWS, THANKS: Update.

